"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.14.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.14.2</span> 標題：異教神廟、偶像的廟（pagan temple, idol’s temple）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bayith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:27\">JDG 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:46\">JDG 9:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:5\">JDG 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:2\">1SA 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:5\">1SA 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:10\">1CH 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:10\">1CH 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:7\">EZR 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:12\">JER 43:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:13\">JER 43:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:2\">DAN 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:14\">NAM 1:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִקְדָּשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： miqdash)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:31\">LEV 26:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:12\">ISA 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:24\">EZK 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:7\">EZK 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:18\">EZK 28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:9\">AMO 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:13\">AMO 7:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： εἰδωλεῖον, εἰδώλιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： eidōleion, eidōlion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:10\">1CO 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:47\">1MA 1:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:83\">1MA 10:83</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd2:7\">1ES 2:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἱερόν, ἱερός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： hieron, hieros)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:27\">ACT 19:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt4:1\">JDT 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:8\">BEL 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:2\">1MA 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:84\">1MA 10:84</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:4\">1MA 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc1:13\">2MA 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc1:15\">2MA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc14:33\">2MA 14:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc2:28\">3MA 2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc3:16\">3MA 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc3:16\">3MA 3:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ναός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： naos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:14\">BEL 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd1:39\">1ES 1:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd6:18\">1ES 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd6:18\">1ES 6:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： οἰκία, οἶκος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： oikia, oikos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:11\">LJE 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:15\">LJE 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:18\">LJE 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:19\">LJE 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:20\">LJE 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:30\">LJE 1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EpJer1:54\">LJE 1:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:10\">BEL 1:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σκηνή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： skēnē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:43\">ACT 7:43</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： τέμενος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： temenos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:47\">1MA 1:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:43\">1MA 5:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:44\">1MA 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc1:15\">2MA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:2\">2MA 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc11:3\">2MA 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc1:7\">3MA 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc1:13\">3MA 1:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>異教神廟是一個供奉偶像的宗教場所，應該至少有一所房子那麼大，甚至比房子大很多。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在上面列出的經文中，希伯來文<em>miqdash</em> 究竟是指非以色列人敬拜的地方，還是指猶太人的聖殿，這一點有時並不清楚；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:7\">EZK 21:7</a> （《和》21:2）中，有些譯本譯為複數的「聖所」（“sanctuaries”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ），還有一些譯本譯為「聖殿」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> ）或單數的「聖所」（“sanctuary”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ），指猶太人的聖殿。</p>\n<p>希臘文詞語<em>eidōleion</em> 和<em>eidōlion</em> 可譯為：「供奉偶像的建築物」，或「敬拜偶像的大房子」。由於「偶像」常被譯為「神明的塑像」（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.6 偶像 (idols)&lt;REALIA:4.6&gt;</a> ），這兩個詞可以譯為：「在裡面敬拜神像的建築物」。有些文化對小型的土地神屋很熟悉。然而，這兩個希臘文詞語指的是比較大的神社，是可供朝拜者進入的。翻譯者選擇譯詞時，注意不要讓讀者以為某人怪異地進入極小的構築物裡面。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:43\">ACT 7:43</a> 中，希臘文<em>skēnē</em> 不是指一棟建築，而是指一個臨時搭建的構築物，一個「帳棚」（“tent”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。在下一節經文中，作者用了同一個詞來指猶太人的帳幕，不過司提反的本意並不是要比較兩者。</p>\n<p>從語言學來說，希臘文<em>temenos</em> 一詞並不是指建築物，而是指一個可能建有廟宇或神龕的特定神聖區域。雖然如此，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:47\">1MA 1:47</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 仍將這個詞譯為“temples”（「廟宇」），而<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 則譯為“sacred precincts”（「神聖的界域」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 譯為“shrines”（「神龕」）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
